================================================================================================================================

README - Egg Production Calculator
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Introduction

The Egg Production Calculator is a Python application designed to help users calculate their earnings and sales from egg production based on the number of active chickens. This application uses the Tkinter library for the GUI and several other libraries for functionality.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Features

Sales Calculation: Calculate the total sales price of the produced eggs.
Wage Calculation: Calculate the wage based on the produced eggs and processing hours.
QR Code Generation: Generate a QR code for a simplified receipt.
Save Receipt: Save the detailed receipt as a text file.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
How to Use

Install Python: Ensure you have Python installed on your system.
Clone Repository: Clone this repository to your local machine.
Navigate to Directory: Open a terminal and navigate to the project directory.
Install Dependencies: Run the following command to install the required dependencies:
pip install -r requirements.txt
Launch Application: Execute the script by running:
python main.py
Enter Data: Input the week number and the number of active chickens.
Calculate Sales and Wage: Click the "Bereken Omzet en Loon" button to see the results.
View Receipt: View the receipt in the text area and scan the QR code for a simplified version.
Save Receipt: The detailed receipt will be saved as a text file in the project directory.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Technologies Used

Python: The core programming language used for development.
Tkinter: A standard GUI library for Python.
qrcode: A Python library for generating QR codes.
Pillow (PIL): A Python Imaging Library (PIL Fork) that adds image processing capabilities.
datetime: A module for working with dates and times.
math: A module providing mathematical functions.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Acknowledgments

Special thanks to the developers and the community behind Python and the used libraries for providing the tools to create this application. Enjoy using the Egg Production Calculator!
Feel free to reach out with any questions or feedback!
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
